Package: libstoragemgmt1
Architecture: any
Multi-Arch: same
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Storage array management library - shared library
 The libStorageMgmt library provides a vendor agnostic open source storage
 application programming interface (API) that allows management of storage
 arrays.

